Title: Admiral Taylor has Awakened
Description:
It would seem that your Admiral Taylor has awakened from his injuries. He and his people are upstairs.

He has requested your presence.
ObjectivesText: Speak with Admiral Taylor at Binan Village in Kun-Lai Summit.
RewardText:
$n, is that you? I can't believe we survived the destruction of the Jade Serpent.

Some of us anyway.
